WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.020 --> 00:00:30.870
Today you all have decided
to have the puja of Adi Shakti.

00:00:30.870 --> 00:00:39.150
There's a difference between doing
the puja of Kundalini Shakti

00:00:39.150 --> 00:00:43.590
or Adi Kundalini and Adi Shakti.

00:00:43.590 --> 00:00:50.280
The difference is like this:
on one side the Kundalini

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:57.510
is reflected in you
by Adi Kundalini.

00:00:57.510 --> 00:01:04.065
The second side is the power
of Adi Shakti which is Paramchaitanya.

00:01:04.065 --> 00:01:09.600
So in totality if you see,
it has two sides:

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:13.890
one is Her power as Paramchaitanya

00:01:13.890 --> 00:01:21.330
and also reflection in human beings
as Kundalini.

00:01:28.440 --> 00:01:36.090
The third work that Adi Shakti
had to do was to create this universe.

00:01:36.090 --> 00:01:41.790
To begin with, as you have seen
yesterday also,

00:01:41.790 --> 00:01:44.460
how the cosmos was created

00:01:44.460 --> 00:01:54.690
and then how this special planet
of Mother Earth was created.

00:01:54.690 --> 00:02:00.960
Now what I have told you
about Adam and Eve

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:09.555
we have found out said by also John
in his Gnostics book.

00:02:09.555 --> 00:02:10.890
It is very surprising.

00:02:10.890 --> 00:02:14.340
They've always told you
that Christ must have told you

00:02:14.340 --> 00:02:16.830
many things but they are
not in the Bible.

00:02:16.830 --> 00:02:25.050
So if you understand
that this Adi Shakti came as a serpent,

00:02:25.050 --> 00:02:29.010
the Adi Kundalini part of Her,

00:02:29.010 --> 00:02:38.370
and told the Adam and Eve,
especially Eve,

00:02:38.370 --> 00:02:49.080
that she should ask for the fruit
of knowledge to be eaten.

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:53.340
And the reason I gave you
is exactly the thing there:

00:02:53.340 --> 00:02:57.780
that the Mother power,
the feminine power

00:02:57.780 --> 00:03:01.200
didn't want Her children
to live like animals

00:03:01.200 --> 00:03:05.370
without understanding what is
the knowledge of the higher realms,

00:03:05.370 --> 00:03:12.300
not giving them chance to rise higher
through their freedom

00:03:12.300 --> 00:03:18.240
and then to higher and higher awareness.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:22.020
It was the concern of the Mother.

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:28.920
So there were two types of worlds
were created:

00:03:28.920 --> 00:03:33.120
one was the Divine
and another one started evolving.

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:39.000
To look at it looks very
tremendous task —

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:42.090
thousands and thousands,
billions and billions of years

00:03:42.090 --> 00:03:48.180
have passed for this kind of work
to be done.

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:57.270
But if you see in modern age
we are going to the moon,

00:03:58.410 --> 00:04:10.410
with such a small effort
and also with such a little time

00:04:10.410 --> 00:04:11.520
you reach there.

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:14.160
Nobody could think
that we would ever be there.

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:19.770
All this has happened
through the human brain.

00:04:19.770 --> 00:04:22.620
Now what is the human brain
after all?

00:04:22.620 --> 00:04:28.140
Human brain is not at all anywhere
near a complete brain,

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:33.270
nor is it used fully.

00:04:34.980 --> 00:04:39.300
It's very little bit used by human beings,

00:04:39.300 --> 00:04:42.990
by which they have achieved
this kind of a flight to the moon.

00:04:42.990 --> 00:04:47.310
Of course there was no purpose in it,
I don't know why they are doing it.

00:04:47.310 --> 00:04:48.810
But they did it.

00:04:56.670 --> 00:05:02.115
So the whole nature was created by Her.

00:05:02.115 --> 00:05:06.840
Whatever you see today
around yourself is all created by Her,

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:10.080
is all Her work that is there.

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:15.390
You'll be amazed —
just now I said I was going to wear

00:05:15.390 --> 00:05:19.200
a very heavy sari
and I said it's very hot,

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:22.440
so better change to a simple sari,
so I changed.

00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:25.230
And when I came out
I found it has become cooler.

00:05:25.230 --> 00:05:33.030
So the nature knows everything

00:05:33.030 --> 00:05:38.340
and who informs the nature
is this Paramchaitanya.

00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:45.240
Paramchaitanya was never that active
as it has been since My birth,

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:47.100
I should say, when Krita Yuga started.

00:05:47.100 --> 00:05:54.060
At this time you had to have
your realisation.

00:05:54.060 --> 00:05:59.280
That was decided by
the Divine collectivity, you can call it.

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:02.580
All the Gods, Goddesses,
all of them decided

00:06:02.580 --> 00:06:09.600
to put this work on somebody
whom they thought to be very capable.

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:15.870
So They said: We will all be with You,
entirely with You,

00:06:15.870 --> 00:06:18.390
all Our powers will be with You,

00:06:18.390 --> 00:06:22.350
but You take up this job now
in this Kali Yuga

00:06:22.350 --> 00:06:25.500
to transform human beings.

00:06:25.500 --> 00:06:30.270
In a way human beings are more difficult
than animals

00:06:30.270 --> 00:06:33.420
because they have their own freedom

00:06:33.420 --> 00:06:39.450
and they have been given this freedom
to achieve their final freedom.

00:06:39.450 --> 00:06:43.230
In their freedom,
the way they behave,

00:06:43.230 --> 00:06:46.395
is something very surprising —

00:06:46.395 --> 00:06:50.100
how they go completely out of control

00:06:50.100 --> 00:06:56.190
and try to do things
which are so destructive.

00:06:56.190 --> 00:07:00.990
Of course in Kali Yuga
it was predicted in India,

00:07:00.990 --> 00:07:05.100
but I think they could not predict
what would happen in America

00:07:05.100 --> 00:07:07.320
or what would happen
in the Western countries

00:07:07.320 --> 00:07:11.370
where people have freedom
just to destroy themselves

00:07:11.370 --> 00:07:16.050
and they're finding new methods
of destroying themselves.

00:07:16.050 --> 00:07:24.690
This tendency cannot be curbed,
cannot be stopped

00:07:24.690 --> 00:07:28.650
by Adi Shakti or by God Almighty,

00:07:28.650 --> 00:07:33.240
because you have been given the freedom
to ruin yourselves,

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:36.090
spoil yourselves and to go to hell.

00:07:36.090 --> 00:07:40.320
That cannot be controlled
by any Divine power.

00:07:40.320 --> 00:07:43.980
Divine power also respects
your freedom.

00:07:43.980 --> 00:07:52.290
So the Divine collectivity thought:
are We going to completely ruin

00:07:52.290 --> 00:07:55.380
the creation of Adi Shakti?

00:07:55.380 --> 00:08:05.010
Are We going to completely destroy
whatever She has created

00:08:05.010 --> 00:08:07.890
and then re-create something better?

00:08:07.890 --> 00:08:10.230
This was the discussion going on.

00:08:10.230 --> 00:08:16.200
And most of Them were so fed up
with the human beings,

00:08:16.200 --> 00:08:18.990
especially with the Western freedom,

00:08:18.990 --> 00:08:21.810
that They said these people want help.

00:08:21.810 --> 00:08:28.410
And why should We give them the Heavens?
It's not proper.

00:08:28.410 --> 00:08:36.870
So first thing Adi Shakti did
was to create a seeking in them.

00:08:36.870 --> 00:08:42.120
She created this desire to seek.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:46.230
And so these people
belonging to this culture

00:08:46.230 --> 00:08:49.440
which was so destructive
started seeking.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:55.020
And when the seeking started,
also, as usual in the market,

00:08:55.020 --> 00:08:57.150
there were many others
who came forward

00:08:57.150 --> 00:08:58.650
to respond to their seeking.

00:08:58.650 --> 00:09:04.980
They had to go to various cults
and things and false people

00:09:04.980 --> 00:09:07.590
and all that, because they had
no way to know.

00:09:07.590 --> 00:09:14.130
But if they had read some books
of enlightened people

00:09:14.130 --> 00:09:24.240
like Kabir, like Nanak,
even Gnostics, their scriptures,

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:28.650
anything like that, they would have
understood what is the truth

00:09:28.650 --> 00:09:32.490
and where to find it
and how to find it.

00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:37.710
It is a big struggle I find

00:09:37.710 --> 00:09:45.390
between the people who are seekers
and those who are not at all seekers.

00:09:45.390 --> 00:09:50.250
They don't want to know
and they can never be seekers.

00:09:50.250 --> 00:09:56.880
I can assure you that some of them
will never think of seeking.

00:09:56.880 --> 00:10:00.540
They'll get possessed,
they'll have diseases,

00:10:00.540 --> 00:10:04.500
they'll have earthquakes,
they'll have anything —

00:10:04.500 --> 00:10:05.730
they will never seek.

00:10:05.730 --> 00:10:10.320
Even if they get diseases,
they'll say,

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:13.050
"Oh, we are martyrs,
we're doing great work."

00:10:13.050 --> 00:10:17.940
Such stupidity has come into their heads

00:10:17.940 --> 00:10:20.550
that they think that by doing
these wrong things,

00:10:20.550 --> 00:10:22.710
we are going to be saved.

00:10:22.710 --> 00:10:29.460
And this stupidity comes
through perverted brains.

00:10:29.460 --> 00:10:36.420
And this perverted brain acts
when people are free to use it.

00:10:36.420 --> 00:10:40.110
I just don't know why they don't
see around themselves

00:10:40.110 --> 00:10:42.390
and see for themselves
what is happening.

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:46.500
So to expect that the whole world
will go to Heaven

00:10:46.500 --> 00:10:50.670
is absolutely not possible,
it cannot.

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:55.050
They have tried all kinds of things.

00:10:55.050 --> 00:11:00.300
I've seen people — drugs,
alcohol, this, that.

00:11:00.300 --> 00:11:06.810
There is one fellow who got his PhD
on writing how he reached spirituality

00:11:06.810 --> 00:11:09.960
through drinking —
and they gave him a PhD for that.

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:15.630
So even at the helm of affairs
in the universities,

00:11:15.630 --> 00:11:20.040
I don't know how such stupid people
came up, from where,

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:21.270
out of which creation.

00:11:21.270 --> 00:11:26.280
It's impossible to understand
how they could think

00:11:26.280 --> 00:11:32.310
that this kind of destruction
will lead them to salvation.

00:11:32.310 --> 00:11:36.630
They see it everyday.
They watch it everyday.

00:11:36.630 --> 00:11:40.800
They know it, it's happening —
but still they cannot listen.

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:46.590
But those who are seekers
are so ardently seeking

00:11:46.590 --> 00:11:50.670
that they will all have to be given
their self-realisation.

00:11:50.670 --> 00:11:54.720
Now this is of course My job,
I agree.

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:57.930
I have come on this earth
for that job.

00:11:57.930 --> 00:11:59.790
I am supposed to do it.

00:11:59.790 --> 00:12:02.310
I am trying my level best

00:12:02.910 --> 00:12:07.050
and no incarnation has lived
like I have lived for so many years,

00:12:07.050 --> 00:12:14.730
and such compassion of Mine
which really makes Me think

00:12:14.730 --> 00:12:18.330
that we have to have
many more Sahaja Yogis,

00:12:18.330 --> 00:12:23.070
we have to have big salvation.

00:12:23.070 --> 00:12:27.270
With that compassion
and with that love,

00:12:27.270 --> 00:12:34.410
one can take to any measures,
anything.

00:12:34.410 --> 00:12:39.480
I do not think those who are
not seekers will achieve it.

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:43.470
Now why is it some are seekers
and some are not?

00:12:43.470 --> 00:12:48.900
One may say that Adi Shakti,
if She has created all human beings,

00:12:48.900 --> 00:12:51.180
all of them should have seeking.

00:12:51.180 --> 00:12:56.640
Because in freedom,
they have lost their way.

00:12:56.640 --> 00:13:02.070
They are seeking something else
and they think they're right.

00:13:02.070 --> 00:13:04.500
They have a right to think
that they are right.

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:08.460
Even a stupid fellow,
even a mad person thinks he's right.

00:13:08.460 --> 00:13:12.150
If you tell him that you are mad,
he'll say: you are mad.

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:21.465
And this seeking, though put into them,
they are not yet capable —

00:13:21.465 --> 00:13:25.830
so many of them —
of achieving it in the proper way.

00:13:25.830 --> 00:13:32.040
Because for that one has to surrender —

00:13:32.040 --> 00:13:35.910
not one's freedom,
not one's intelligence,

00:13:35.910 --> 00:13:40.290
but the ego that has developed
in human beings.

00:13:40.290 --> 00:13:44.730
With this ego, even people
who are possessed

00:13:44.730 --> 00:13:46.080
want to keep their ego intact

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:51.720
and through the ego
they want to use their possessions.

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:52.800
Can you imagine?

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:56.520
There are possessions
of negative forces.

00:13:56.520 --> 00:14:05.010
Such people want to keep that intact
so that they can use it

00:14:05.010 --> 00:14:07.200
for their own purpose.

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:12.630
They don't hate it,
they don't want to get rid of it.

00:14:12.630 --> 00:14:18.150
But they want to keep it
just because they can use it.

00:14:18.150 --> 00:14:22.860
So the category of seeking
is much less there.

00:14:22.860 --> 00:14:29.085
But there are many who are
nowhere near seeking —

00:14:29.085 --> 00:14:32.580
who are really what we call
the evil people —

00:14:32.580 --> 00:14:38.250
and they would never want
this world to change.

00:14:38.250 --> 00:14:41.700
Our media is dominated
by these evil people.

00:14:41.700 --> 00:14:44.250
They don't want the world to change.

00:14:44.250 --> 00:14:46.890
They don't want to show anything
that is good.

00:14:46.890 --> 00:14:51.810
They don't want to see
what is going to help,

00:14:51.810 --> 00:14:54.120
what is benevolent for human beings.

00:14:54.120 --> 00:15:06.190
So on one side, we see
such collective negativity.

00:15:06.190 --> 00:15:12.190
On another side we find seekers
who are real seekers.

00:15:12.190 --> 00:15:17.650
There are some we can call half-baked
and some are pseudo seekers.

00:15:21.100 --> 00:15:29.950
And in the name of seeking,
if they have made some sacrifice,

00:15:33.490 --> 00:15:34.420
they feel very great.

00:15:34.420 --> 00:15:41.920
Also they get involved with people
who are making claims.

00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:48.370
Because I have never claimed anything,
they are not impressed by me.

00:15:48.370 --> 00:15:52.210
I've not changed my dress.
I live like a housewife.

00:15:52.210 --> 00:15:55.000
So they are not impressed by me.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:59.860
I have not developed anything unusual
to show something great about myself

00:15:59.860 --> 00:16:01.420
so they won't be impressed.

00:16:01.420 --> 00:16:07.360
But on the other side if you see,
this is maya, this is Mahamaya,

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:13.600
where Adi Shakti does everything
like human beings do, everything.

00:16:13.600 --> 00:16:17.350
You won't be able to find out
that She is Divine.

00:16:17.350 --> 00:16:22.960
My family people could not find out
till I started this work,

00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:25.180
none of them,
except for my father and mother.

00:16:25.180 --> 00:16:31.660
Nobody could find out
that I had any powers.

00:16:31.660 --> 00:16:41.920
Such insensitivity to the Divine
can be created by the Mahamaya power

00:16:41.920 --> 00:16:45.760
of Adi Shakti, which is very important —

00:16:45.760 --> 00:16:49.630
otherwise you cannot judge,
you cannot understand.

00:16:49.630 --> 00:16:52.810
Despite that, I've many times
misjudged people

00:16:52.810 --> 00:16:59.740
because they know how to camouflage
for a little while.

00:16:59.740 --> 00:17:01.300
But then I discover.

00:17:01.300 --> 00:17:09.760
If the seeking is ardent
and they are truly seeking the truth,

00:17:10.540 --> 00:17:14.770
they will find it, they will find it —
no doubt —

00:17:14.770 --> 00:17:17.050
because the whole creation
is for them.

00:17:17.050 --> 00:17:21.790
The whole universe is for them.

00:17:21.790 --> 00:17:26.830
All Deities are for them.
All angels are for them.

00:17:26.830 --> 00:17:29.890
They are all looking out for them.

00:17:29.890 --> 00:17:36.280
This is important —
that we have so many Sahaja Yogis.

00:17:36.280 --> 00:17:42.010
Nobody had so many Sahaja Yogis
in their lifetime.

00:17:42.010 --> 00:17:46.390
Because we have to have channels.

00:17:46.390 --> 00:17:49.090
I have to have channels

00:17:49.090 --> 00:17:55.270
and these channels have to be
very clean, beautiful, innocent,

00:17:55.270 --> 00:17:57.580
and benevolent.

00:17:57.580 --> 00:18:06.400
If only they surrender to this fact

00:18:06.400 --> 00:18:12.040
that we are here as instruments
of God Almighty

00:18:12.040 --> 00:18:16.690
and that we have to give
benevolence to others —

00:18:16.690 --> 00:18:22.840
I tell you, at least 70% of work
is done.

00:18:22.840 --> 00:18:31.420
But even if they have got realisation,

00:18:31.420 --> 00:18:37.690
like an egg comes out of the shell,

00:18:37.690 --> 00:18:43.150
some of the birds still carry
part of the egg

00:18:43.150 --> 00:18:47.650
and some of them are not even grown
up to be birds.

00:18:47.650 --> 00:18:56.680
Now we have to judge ourselves.
We have to understand ourselves.

00:18:56.680 --> 00:19:04.750
Another thing — you know that
I'm a very mild person, very mild.

00:19:04.750 --> 00:19:10.750
People think I'm very forgiving.
I know everyone, not that I don't.

00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:16.600
But I allow — alright, go ahead,
as far as you can go.

00:19:16.600 --> 00:19:21.080
Experience is the only way
a human being can understand,

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:21.890
no doubt.

00:19:21.890 --> 00:19:25.340
If you tell him something,
he will never understand.

00:19:25.340 --> 00:19:29.840
Experience of self-realisation
has made you understand.

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:37.220
But again, I would say
that we cannot give realisation

00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:38.480
to the whole world, we cannot.

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:44.360
They're like stones,
absolutely horrible people.

00:19:44.360 --> 00:19:51.140
Whatever is happening is that
those who are false are getting exposed.

00:19:51.140 --> 00:19:55.520
And everybody is noticing
that they are getting exposed.

00:19:55.520 --> 00:20:01.760
This exposure will of course save them
from these horrible people.

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:04.460
But I don't know if they will come
to Sahaja Yoga

00:20:04.460 --> 00:20:07.010
or if they would take
their realisation.

00:20:09.500 --> 00:20:15.290
I'm telling you this because now
I have the experience of human beings

00:20:15.290 --> 00:20:18.080
and all these years I have been working,

00:20:18.080 --> 00:20:23.540
I have seen that there are
people and people and people.

00:20:23.540 --> 00:20:32.600
Out of them, the seekers are
extremely proud of their seeking.

00:20:32.600 --> 00:20:38.990
So some of them don't want
to give up their seeking —

00:20:38.990 --> 00:20:40.310
it's a kind of a job.

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:45.620
You can call it a hobby —
they are seekers.

00:20:45.620 --> 00:20:49.700
Now they have a certificate
of being a seeker.

00:20:49.700 --> 00:20:53.990
They wear funny dresses,
have funny houses, funny hair,

00:20:53.990 --> 00:20:58.610
everything — recluses they could be,
aggressive, anything —

00:20:58.610 --> 00:20:59.450
"we are seekers."

00:20:59.450 --> 00:21:03.620
They take a certificate
upon themselves: we are seekers.

00:21:03.620 --> 00:21:07.220
This is another quality
of seekers also.

00:21:08.210 --> 00:21:11.240
For them it's a kind of lifestyle.

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:17.495
They're seekers and wherever they have
to go, they will go for seeking —

00:21:17.495 --> 00:21:19.520
they'll go to 10 places, or 20 places.

00:21:19.520 --> 00:21:25.310
Every time they have argued with me,
"Mother there must be some more ways" —

00:21:25.310 --> 00:21:29.490
yes, maybe, I don't know of any,
you can find out.

00:21:29.490 --> 00:21:38.940
Now the main job of Adi Shakti today
is to give realisation.

00:21:38.940 --> 00:21:40.920
That's My main job.

00:21:40.920 --> 00:21:46.140
All the rest is looked after —
it's already managed,

00:21:47.130 --> 00:21:48.060
like a computer.

00:21:48.060 --> 00:21:51.930
I don't have to work it,
it's a reflex action.

00:21:51.930 --> 00:21:55.230
Whatever is happening
is in a reflex action.

00:21:55.230 --> 00:21:57.780
I don't have to worry
about these things.

00:21:59.550 --> 00:22:04.920
Like people might say,
"Mother I prayed to you

00:22:04.920 --> 00:22:08.670
and how is it you helped me
so much?"

00:22:08.670 --> 00:22:10.800
It's all reflex action.

00:22:12.450 --> 00:22:15.746
That thought may come to Me
at that moment,

00:22:15.746 --> 00:22:16.470
but it's reflex action.

00:22:16.470 --> 00:22:18.180
I really don't do anything.

00:22:18.180 --> 00:22:22.500
Actually, I'm just witnessing.
Not doing anything whatsoever.

00:22:22.500 --> 00:22:30.660
The laziest person you could think of
is Me, really.

00:22:30.660 --> 00:22:35.520
Because if there's a complete
organisation working for Me,

00:22:35.520 --> 00:22:40.590
why should I do anything.

00:22:41.220 --> 00:22:45.360
But one thing is there — I'm witnessing.

00:22:45.360 --> 00:22:53.550
And when I'm witnessing,
that acts on the reflex,

00:22:53.550 --> 00:22:57.930
that works out the Paramchaitanya.

00:22:57.930 --> 00:23:02.100
Because if that is the power
of the Adi Shakti,

00:23:02.100 --> 00:23:11.610
then whatever I witness
gets reported to that power.

00:23:11.610 --> 00:23:14.295
It's the other way round —

00:23:14.295 --> 00:23:28.590
like electricity: if something goes wrong
here, it finishes off here.

00:23:28.590 --> 00:23:31.140
But the other way round —

00:23:31.140 --> 00:23:36.570
if I witness something wrong,
I don't have to do anything,

00:23:36.570 --> 00:23:38.100
I just witness, I'm just watching,

00:23:39.860 --> 00:23:46.610
the whole thing acts through
this tremendous power of Paramchaitanya.

00:23:46.610 --> 00:23:51.770
Now this power you do not know.

00:23:51.770 --> 00:23:55.790
You know Kundalini, you know all
about chakras, this, that,

00:23:55.790 --> 00:24:06.200
but this power of Paramchaitanya
is in every particle in you,

00:24:06.200 --> 00:24:07.850
every atom.

00:24:07.850 --> 00:24:25.460
And it acts in such a manner
that it directs, it pushes you,

00:24:25.460 --> 00:24:32.300
it takes you to the path
of benevolence.

00:24:32.300 --> 00:24:36.830
Sometimes people say,
"Mother I wanted to buy this shop,

00:24:36.830 --> 00:24:38.240
I couldn't get it" and all that.

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:42.080
It is for your benevolence
you didn't get it — thank God.

00:24:42.080 --> 00:24:46.940
After 10 days they'll come and say,
thank God I didn't get it.

00:24:46.940 --> 00:24:53.510
So gradually through experience,
you start understanding

00:24:53.510 --> 00:24:55.580
that you don't have to worry.

00:24:55.580 --> 00:25:01.460
If you are lost on the way,
normally people get very upset,

00:25:01.460 --> 00:25:03.165
but Sahaja Yogis don't —

00:25:03.165 --> 00:25:07.610
"oh, very nice, must be something here
that God has brought us."

00:25:07.610 --> 00:25:13.610
This reaction then changes.

00:25:13.610 --> 00:25:19.250
I would say the person
who is overactive

00:25:19.250 --> 00:25:26.600
starts thinking now:
surrender, Islam, surrender.

00:25:26.600 --> 00:25:33.170
Give this problem
to this Paramchaitanya

00:25:33.860 --> 00:25:36.260
and it works.

00:25:36.260 --> 00:25:46.190
Such tremendous things have happened
in this world just by bandhans

00:25:46.190 --> 00:25:54.020
that it is unbelievable
how these things are happening.

00:25:54.020 --> 00:26:04.910
Even so many murders,
this thing has happened,

00:26:04.910 --> 00:26:06.110
that has happened —

00:26:06.110 --> 00:26:11.060
this is also just to express
the presence of Paramchaitanya,

00:26:13.250 --> 00:26:15.890
it's working out.

00:26:20.750 --> 00:26:25.520
Then you start realising
that this power

00:26:25.520 --> 00:26:30.530
you can achieve
through your Kundalini.

00:26:30.530 --> 00:26:35.240
So when your Kundalini rises,

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:41.180
that is also a reflection
of Adi Shakti.

00:26:41.180 --> 00:26:45.080
Like we can say, we see one part
of the moon, the other part we don't.

00:26:45.080 --> 00:26:51.740
In the same way, this power
when it rises within you

00:26:51.740 --> 00:27:00.590
and touches this Paramchaitanya,
you become empowered by that.

00:27:00.590 --> 00:27:06.950
That's how you are Sahaja Yogis.

00:27:06.950 --> 00:27:09.560
But you are not God.

00:27:09.560 --> 00:27:15.320
The incarnations can say,
"I am God."

00:27:15.320 --> 00:27:18.500
You are not incarnations.

00:27:18.500 --> 00:27:28.970
But none of the incarnations have
ever said that they are Adi Shakti —

00:27:28.970 --> 00:27:31.340
cannot.

00:27:31.910 --> 00:27:36.740
This power of Adi Shakti
which we call Paramchaitanya

00:27:36.740 --> 00:27:44.780
is the power that loves you,
has complete control of the nature.

00:27:44.780 --> 00:27:54.950
It understands, it thinks,
it knows everything about you.

00:27:55.970 --> 00:28:06.110
It works in every angle,
in every walk of your life.

00:28:06.110 --> 00:28:10.145
It is with you entirely —

00:28:10.145 --> 00:28:16.550
as if you fall into a river
which is flowing fast

00:28:16.550 --> 00:28:22.070
and you cannot swim anymore,

00:28:22.070 --> 00:28:27.440
you start flowing with it

00:28:27.440 --> 00:28:31.970
and then you realise that flowing
with it is a better thing

00:28:31.970 --> 00:28:33.890
than to try to get out of it.

00:28:36.050 --> 00:28:42.500
Just flowing with it,
just enjoy all the nature around you.

00:28:42.500 --> 00:28:43.460
You don't get drowned.

00:28:43.460 --> 00:28:46.010
On the contrary, you feel elevated.

00:28:46.010 --> 00:28:51.020
And you're flowing with it —
then you understand:

00:28:51.020 --> 00:28:55.220
what am I to do about something,
whether it's done by Paramchaitanya.

00:28:56.120 --> 00:29:03.800
But that it should be given
to your Kundalini

00:29:03.800 --> 00:29:05.750
which has worked it out,

00:29:05.750 --> 00:29:08.180
has put you onto that shore,

00:29:08.180 --> 00:29:15.680
has put you onto that beautiful
Heavenly Kingdom of God.

00:29:15.680 --> 00:29:20.900
Thus you understand there are two things
that have happened:

00:29:21.440 --> 00:29:24.050
first, your Mother, your Kundalini
which is within you,

00:29:24.050 --> 00:29:28.130
which is your own Mother,
which has been with you throughout,

00:29:28.130 --> 00:29:29.960
has given you this birth.

00:29:29.960 --> 00:29:33.470
And then it has taken you
to that power,

00:29:33.470 --> 00:29:38.060
which power you can use yourself.

00:29:38.060 --> 00:29:40.700
You are empowered by that.

00:29:40.700 --> 00:29:44.480
You'll be amazed how this power helps.

00:29:45.020 --> 00:29:52.730
I mean, you see —
I shouldn't say that you can have

00:29:52.730 --> 00:29:54.320
all the powers, I shouldn't say that.

00:29:54.320 --> 00:29:58.190
But today — they were complaining
about somebody,

00:29:58.190 --> 00:29:59.840
immediately I told the name
of the person.

00:29:59.840 --> 00:30:02.570
Now you'll say, how did I know.

00:30:02.570 --> 00:30:06.020
I just know. That's all I can say.

00:30:07.010 --> 00:30:10.760
Supposing you are dealing
with carpets —

00:30:10.760 --> 00:30:13.880
so you know what pattern is this,
what pattern is that,

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:19.280
from where it has come —
everything, you know, isn't it.

00:30:19.280 --> 00:30:22.460
If you are in that field,
you know everything.

00:30:22.460 --> 00:30:29.300
If this power is everywhere,
one has to know everything.

00:30:29.810 --> 00:30:34.400
The connection is such.
If you want to know, you can know.

00:30:34.400 --> 00:30:41.540
So they have called also Buddha
as Avalokiteshvara —

00:30:41.540 --> 00:30:44.210
that He sees all the lotuses.

00:30:44.210 --> 00:30:50.930
How does He see — Avalokiteshvara —
because His ego,

00:30:50.930 --> 00:31:02.120
what we call the paramaego,
the Mahatahamkara,

00:31:03.620 --> 00:31:05.930
knows everything,

00:31:05.930 --> 00:31:09.470
while your ego
doesn't know anything.

00:31:09.470 --> 00:31:20.990
Because it doesn't know anything,
you are enveloped by it.

00:31:20.990 --> 00:31:29.870
If the ego had known the truth,
you'll be a free person, absolutely free.

00:31:29.870 --> 00:31:33.440
But you don't want to surrender
your ego.

00:31:33.440 --> 00:31:40.220
You don't want to allow yourself
to flow into the river as Tao.

00:31:41.150 --> 00:31:48.380
No — you want to have
your own speciality.

00:31:48.380 --> 00:31:56.840
Individuality is very different
from having an ego within yourself

00:31:56.840 --> 00:31:57.800
that says: I am this, I am that.

00:31:57.800 --> 00:32:05.870
So this differentiation must start,
after realisation,

00:32:05.870 --> 00:32:11.030
in the light of realisation,
you should start seeing.

00:32:11.030 --> 00:32:16.400
Now the first and foremost thing
is to tell your ego

00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:19.250
to sit down, keep quiet.

00:32:19.250 --> 00:32:25.310
And also in the modern times
it's a big fashion —

00:32:25.310 --> 00:32:27.050
you ask somebody,
"I don't know."

00:32:27.050 --> 00:32:31.250
You ask somebody, what's your name,
"I don't know."

00:32:31.250 --> 00:32:33.710
He doesn't even know his name.

00:32:33.710 --> 00:32:38.900
And to be stupid is a fashion.

00:32:38.900 --> 00:32:46.355
To show that you are very stupid
they think they are showing innocence.

00:32:46.355 --> 00:32:50.582
It's not — it's stupidity.

00:32:50.582 --> 00:32:52.700
This stupidity —
I don't know which animal has it.

00:32:52.700 --> 00:32:54.860
Still I don't know
what is the source of it.

00:33:03.020 --> 00:33:07.340
But I know one thing — it is our ego.

00:33:07.340 --> 00:33:12.470
Ego makes a person
absolutely stupid.

00:33:12.470 --> 00:33:18.500
In Marathi, thank God,
the language is so rich

00:33:18.500 --> 00:33:22.910
that anybody who starts showing off
his ego,

00:33:22.910 --> 00:33:23.691
they say he's climbing on a bush —

00:33:23.691 --> 00:33:26.930
there is a little bush
and he is climbing on it.

00:33:28.640 --> 00:33:41.150
All this ego comes through
your own so-called ideas,

00:33:41.150 --> 00:33:42.620
achievements.

00:33:42.620 --> 00:33:49.130
But what are these achievements?
You don't know anything.

00:33:53.220 --> 00:33:56.340
And this is what today I have to
tell you —

00:33:56.340 --> 00:34:01.800
that if anything is working out today,
it is your surrender of your ego.

00:34:01.800 --> 00:34:06.630
If you know how to surrender
your ego, you'll work it out.

00:34:06.630 --> 00:34:11.490
Another thing which surprises me
sometimes, in the West especially,

00:34:11.490 --> 00:34:15.570
is that I think women are the power —
they are the Shakti.

00:34:15.570 --> 00:34:27.810
But in the West I find women
are not using Adi Shakti, no.

00:34:27.810 --> 00:34:39.210
Firstly, they are still very much
possessed by their emotions

00:34:39.210 --> 00:34:43.950
and by their ideas and things like that.

00:34:43.950 --> 00:34:46.710
One side is man, who is doing
everything.

00:34:46.710 --> 00:34:52.530
But even women are very egoistical,
very much. It's very difficult.

00:34:52.530 --> 00:35:00.180
For example, you marry some girl,
a Western girl, to somebody.

00:35:00.180 --> 00:35:04.920
She'll be very happy, jumping,
taking all the presents,

00:35:04.920 --> 00:35:07.980
congratulations, wearing all the dress,
everything.

00:35:07.980 --> 00:35:14.730
After 10 days, she'll come
and say, "Mother I'm confused."

00:35:14.730 --> 00:35:16.380
Confused, how?

00:35:16.380 --> 00:35:18.930
"I'm now confused."

00:35:18.930 --> 00:35:21.780
You're confused now or before?

00:35:21.780 --> 00:35:23.460
"I'm now confused."

00:35:23.460 --> 00:35:26.190
Alright — you return all
your ornaments and everything.

00:35:26.190 --> 00:35:27.240
"No, no, then let me think."

00:35:27.240 --> 00:35:33.660
This is not the level
of a Sahaja Yogini.

00:35:33.660 --> 00:35:38.730
Sahaja Yogini is the Shakti

00:35:38.730 --> 00:35:45.270
and she has to take up challenges —
I'll show you, I'll do it better.

00:35:45.270 --> 00:35:49.650
On the contrary I find them
extremely dominating —

00:35:49.650 --> 00:35:54.000
I'm amazed, why should Shakti dominate?

00:35:54.000 --> 00:35:56.550
If she's Shakti, she will not dominate.

00:35:56.550 --> 00:35:59.070
Those who are not Shakti
will dominate.

00:35:59.070 --> 00:36:05.030
Like if you go in India
to any collector's house,

00:36:05.030 --> 00:36:09.950
the collector will be humble
but the constable would be dominating.

00:36:09.950 --> 00:36:17.360
In the same way,
this domination business is very common.

00:36:17.360 --> 00:36:26.660
And also a kind of temperament
like a nun.

00:36:26.660 --> 00:36:30.170
They'll dress up like a nun,
behave like a nun.

00:36:30.920 --> 00:36:33.830
They won't smile. What is?

00:36:33.830 --> 00:36:37.430
Are you Sahaja Yoginis?
Or are you nuns?

00:36:37.430 --> 00:36:38.690
Then better join a nunnery.

00:36:38.690 --> 00:36:42.590
Why am I talking about this
while talking about Adi Shakti?

00:36:42.590 --> 00:36:47.270
Because I'm talking about Shakti —
how the Shakti has to come up.

00:36:47.270 --> 00:36:52.310
I was surprised that women were not
spreading Sahaja Yoga.

00:36:53.630 --> 00:36:56.810
Somebody told me that the leaders
do not want women to spread it.

00:36:56.810 --> 00:37:01.070
This is wrong.
If the leaders say that, it's not proper.

00:37:01.070 --> 00:37:09.260
But first of all the Sahaja Yoginis
have to be real Sahaja Yoginis.

00:37:09.260 --> 00:37:12.755
Because so far I've seen —

00:37:12.755 --> 00:37:17.840
if you try to give any lady
the position of a leader,

00:37:17.840 --> 00:37:21.230
she just finishes off the thing.

00:37:21.230 --> 00:37:25.310
Not all, but some.

00:37:25.310 --> 00:37:35.750
Now the duty of a Sahaja Yogini
is to develop herself

00:37:35.750 --> 00:37:44.030
through meditation,
through understanding oneself,

00:37:44.030 --> 00:37:46.655
and through self-esteem —

00:37:46.655 --> 00:37:52.100
that I'm a Sahaja Yogini,
I'm the one who is Shakti,

00:37:52.100 --> 00:37:54.290
I'm the potential of that.

00:37:54.290 --> 00:37:56.870
I'm the potential myself.

00:37:56.870 --> 00:37:58.700
What do I do — nothing?

00:37:58.700 --> 00:38:01.475
I didn't do like this,
I didn't put this on —

00:38:01.475 --> 00:38:02.060
nothing of the kind.

00:38:02.060 --> 00:38:03.560
I'm visiting and talking.

00:38:03.560 --> 00:38:11.240
But am I the potential?

00:38:11.240 --> 00:38:16.670
This is what the Sahaja Yoginis
have to decide.

00:38:16.670 --> 00:38:22.580
Otherwise, they're possessed,
they're daydreaming,

00:38:22.580 --> 00:38:25.040
thinking no end of themselves.

00:38:25.040 --> 00:38:27.140
It's very difficult.

00:38:27.140 --> 00:38:33.290
I want some nice Sahaja Yoginis
to be the leaders, I really want.

00:38:33.290 --> 00:38:39.950
But as soon as they become a leader,
they are on a horse, running so fast.

00:38:39.950 --> 00:38:42.650
So be humble, downwards.

00:38:42.650 --> 00:38:51.080
Unless and until there is a big space
in the pitcher,

00:38:51.080 --> 00:38:53.120
what water can flow into it?

00:38:53.120 --> 00:38:56.030
Have a very large heart.

00:38:56.030 --> 00:39:00.080
Anybody comes to your house —
you don't like it,

00:39:00.080 --> 00:39:04.760
you don't want to do anything
for other Sahaja Yogis,

00:39:04.760 --> 00:39:06.110
not looking after them.

00:39:06.110 --> 00:39:12.020
It is really — again and again
I say in the West —

00:39:12.020 --> 00:39:15.140
that women have to take up
Shakti unto themselves.

00:39:15.140 --> 00:39:17.870
And Shakti doesn't mean
dominate your husband

00:39:17.870 --> 00:39:19.010
and make a fool out of him.

00:39:19.010 --> 00:39:22.190
No, it means give him powers.

00:39:22.190 --> 00:39:26.690
You are the supply of power
of the whole family.

00:39:26.690 --> 00:39:32.180
And this is our family.
All this is my family.

00:39:32.180 --> 00:39:33.740
I'm so concerned about everyone.

00:39:33.740 --> 00:39:36.410
Even the little things I'm bothered about.

00:39:36.410 --> 00:39:41.840
I'm never satisfied that I've done
my job now

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:45.440
and I can tonight go off to sleep
and not think of anyone.

00:39:45.440 --> 00:39:47.060
Never.

00:39:47.060 --> 00:39:50.660
I'm concerned about this,
I'm concerned about that.

00:39:50.660 --> 00:39:54.590
All the time it's flowing,
this power,

00:39:54.590 --> 00:39:59.735
and My concern —
this is the power that works —

00:39:59.735 --> 00:40:02.270
because My concern is genuine.

00:40:02.270 --> 00:40:05.180
I'm not concerned about Myself, never.

00:40:05.180 --> 00:40:09.680
You'll be amazed —
when I see all these women

00:40:09.680 --> 00:40:13.130
doing all kinds of things
to themselves, I'm surprised.

00:40:13.930 --> 00:40:17.680
What is needed is the concern.

00:40:17.680 --> 00:40:25.180
And once you develop that concern —
a genuine, loving, compassionate concern

00:40:25.180 --> 00:40:25.750
about others.

00:40:25.750 --> 00:40:30.820
Even about children —
I've seen that they never look after

00:40:30.820 --> 00:40:31.480
each other's children.

00:40:31.480 --> 00:40:34.270
They never help others.

00:40:34.270 --> 00:40:36.610
Somebody had to go
for taking out a tooth

00:40:36.610 --> 00:40:40.510
and she had to carry the child
with her. This is true.

00:40:40.510 --> 00:40:47.530
If you do not have concern,
then you'll not have collective mind,

00:40:47.530 --> 00:40:49.540
you'll not have the collective power.

00:40:49.540 --> 00:40:54.970
And it's important that you all
should try to be very collective,

00:40:54.970 --> 00:40:56.260
look after each other.

00:40:56.260 --> 00:41:00.025
Now I shouldn't say this —
I was going to tell it

00:41:00.025 --> 00:41:01.300
to the Cabella ladies —

00:41:01.300 --> 00:41:03.880
that this house in Cabella is an ashram

00:41:03.880 --> 00:41:06.850
and those people who come
from other ashrams,

00:41:06.850 --> 00:41:08.860
even from Australia, are surprised

00:41:08.860 --> 00:41:12.220
that they are all living here
just like a hotel.

00:41:12.220 --> 00:41:14.890
They're paying for it, we all pay,

00:41:14.890 --> 00:41:18.190
but we have gardens,
we look after the gardens,

00:41:18.190 --> 00:41:19.450
we look after the outside.

00:41:19.450 --> 00:41:20.890
Here nobody's bothered.

00:41:20.890 --> 00:41:25.750
They're using everything,
not bothered.

00:41:25.750 --> 00:41:29.680
Surprisingly, why —
when I'm living here —

00:41:29.680 --> 00:41:30.190
are they like this?

00:41:30.190 --> 00:41:35.110
You go to any place in Australia,
you go to America, anywhere,

00:41:35.110 --> 00:41:38.170
wherever there's an ashram,
they all work on Sundays.

00:41:40.000 --> 00:41:42.040
Here I've not seen that.
They all disappear.

00:41:42.040 --> 00:41:46.210
This is your ashram.
You are staying here.

00:41:46.210 --> 00:41:49.180
And today I have to say this

00:41:49.180 --> 00:41:55.060
because I feel that Sahaja Yoga
is missing out on their Shaktis.

00:41:55.060 --> 00:41:59.380
Some of them do not know
how to smile.

00:41:59.380 --> 00:42:02.830
And some of them
are extremely dominating.

00:42:02.830 --> 00:42:06.700
I have to tell you this
because you are so important.

00:42:06.700 --> 00:42:10.090
But for Me, no man would have
done this job.

00:42:10.090 --> 00:42:13.270
No male incarnation would have
done this job.

00:42:13.270 --> 00:42:16.960
Christ — he got crucified
at a young age, very nice.

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:20.290
Get crucified at such a young age —

00:42:20.290 --> 00:42:26.050
then another one takes to poison,
another one is killed by somebody.

00:42:26.050 --> 00:42:29.105
It's like that — they all died
very young.

00:42:29.105 --> 00:42:35.090
Nobody wanted to do this work,
they got fed up.

00:42:36.530 --> 00:42:41.240
We had Ganeshwara who went
into Samadhi at the age of 23 years —

00:42:41.240 --> 00:42:41.780
can you imagine?

00:42:41.780 --> 00:42:44.390
He must have been fed up
with the people.

00:42:44.390 --> 00:42:52.430
Now it is for you people, the ladies,
to develop that patience of your Mother,

00:42:52.430 --> 00:42:55.100
that affection, that love —

00:42:55.100 --> 00:42:58.535
and then you will see
how your Shakti will work out.

00:42:58.535 --> 00:43:03.650
I again and again have talked
about this.

00:43:03.650 --> 00:43:06.680
And at this Adi Shakti puja,
I have to say:

00:43:06.680 --> 00:43:10.310
you are in your family like a Shakti.

00:43:10.310 --> 00:43:15.350
And you have to be wise,
you have to be sensible.

00:43:15.350 --> 00:43:19.040
You have to understand your husband.
You have to understand your children.

00:43:19.040 --> 00:43:20.330
You have to have patience.

00:43:20.330 --> 00:43:22.880
On the contrary, they spoil
their children.

00:43:22.880 --> 00:43:26.930
That is to be understood —

00:43:26.930 --> 00:43:29.720
you must know first
what is good for their benevolence.

00:43:29.720 --> 00:43:36.560
Today for example, if I say
the children should go to school,

00:43:36.560 --> 00:43:37.970
they should not be removed.

00:43:37.970 --> 00:43:40.550
It is for their benevolence.

00:43:40.550 --> 00:43:43.640
What are people going to gain out of it?

00:43:43.640 --> 00:43:47.660
So somebody says no. Alright, get out.

00:43:47.660 --> 00:43:49.910
What can you do?

00:43:49.910 --> 00:43:57.050
Such attachment to your own children
shows you are a powerless person.

00:43:57.050 --> 00:44:02.870
You must love all the children,
you must look after all the children,

00:44:02.870 --> 00:44:08.180
you must enjoy all the children,
take interest.

00:44:08.180 --> 00:44:13.580
But what I find is that they are only
interested in their own children.

00:44:13.580 --> 00:44:19.580
We are a joint family.
We live together.

00:44:19.580 --> 00:44:28.640
We have to share everything.
It is something I can't understand.

00:44:28.640 --> 00:44:34.070
Say, in India, if you see
5 or 6 children,

00:44:34.070 --> 00:44:36.350
all the girls will run after them.

00:44:36.350 --> 00:44:40.490
All the women will look after them.

00:44:40.490 --> 00:44:42.800
It's such a pleasure to them —
to look after any children.

00:44:44.000 --> 00:44:52.040
But this kind of insensitivity
to your collective behaviour

00:44:52.040 --> 00:44:54.590
is going to also spoil your children.

00:44:54.590 --> 00:44:59.300
So what you are going to transmit
to the whole world

00:44:59.300 --> 00:45:05.645
is this Sahaja living —

00:45:05.645 --> 00:45:09.320
and the women make the society.

00:45:09.320 --> 00:45:13.130
If Indian society is good,
the credit goes to the Indian women

00:45:13.130 --> 00:45:14.090
and their wisdom.

00:45:15.410 --> 00:45:16.700
Men are stupid in India.

00:45:16.700 --> 00:45:19.940
They spoil politics, economics,
everything.

00:45:19.940 --> 00:45:23.720
But society is still maintained

00:45:23.720 --> 00:45:29.900
and they are still on
the right path.

00:45:29.900 --> 00:45:34.130
This only comes because of
the wisdom of the women.

00:45:34.130 --> 00:45:38.000
If the women are busy dressing up
for hours together,

00:45:38.000 --> 00:45:41.915
thinking about their clothes,
what they're going to wear —

00:45:41.915 --> 00:45:42.650
finished.

00:45:42.650 --> 00:45:54.980
This is a day of worshipping
the Kundalini who is the Mother.

00:45:54.980 --> 00:46:01.220
She is the Mother.
And you are the mother.

00:46:01.220 --> 00:46:04.460
You must know each and everything
about your child.

00:46:04.460 --> 00:46:08.600
Somebody comes and tells me,
"My child is now a drug addict."

00:46:08.600 --> 00:46:09.830
How can that be possible?

00:46:09.830 --> 00:46:13.850
In India children don't get addicted
to drugs

00:46:13.850 --> 00:46:17.090
because all the time the mother
is on their head like a hawk.

00:46:17.090 --> 00:46:21.890
She knows where he goes,
what he does — she loves.

00:46:21.890 --> 00:46:25.730
But she knows, very well.

00:46:27.170 --> 00:46:30.350
Even when we are in college,
even when I'm married,

00:46:30.350 --> 00:46:32.960
we went home — my mother would ask,
"Where did you go?

00:46:35.480 --> 00:46:37.700
Did I not say, come back by 6?"

00:46:37.700 --> 00:46:39.110
Even when we were married.

00:46:39.110 --> 00:46:44.840
And we were supposed to tell her.

00:46:44.840 --> 00:46:47.976
That was the mother's work —

00:46:47.976 --> 00:46:50.960
to know where the child goes,
what does he do.

00:46:50.960 --> 00:46:54.290
And then to say
"children don't listen to me" —

00:46:54.290 --> 00:46:56.870
why do children not listen?

00:46:56.870 --> 00:46:59.465
Because you do not discipline them.

00:46:59.465 --> 00:47:03.500
Here the atmosphere is very bad,
agreed,

00:47:03.500 --> 00:47:06.080
and the children are very bad,
agreed.

00:47:06.080 --> 00:47:07.610
Everything is there, agreed.

00:47:07.610 --> 00:47:12.320
But if you are a strong mother
in your love,

00:47:12.320 --> 00:47:15.080
your children will not wander.

00:47:15.080 --> 00:47:21.560
See, even now — all the time
there are all these leaders

00:47:21.560 --> 00:47:23.810
hovering around Me —
what is there?

00:47:23.810 --> 00:47:27.500
I have no honey with me or anything
but they are just sitting there,

00:47:27.500 --> 00:47:31.220
just sitting next to Me,
all the leaders.

00:47:31.220 --> 00:47:34.250
But this is after realisation —

00:47:34.250 --> 00:47:39.590
and even all My nephews, you see,
they would all come

00:47:39.590 --> 00:47:40.640
and sit next to Me.

00:47:40.640 --> 00:47:45.140
All My daughters-in-law
would sit next to Me,

00:47:45.140 --> 00:47:48.110
they would not leave Me.

00:47:48.110 --> 00:47:50.390
And people would say,
"What's wrong with you?

00:47:50.390 --> 00:47:53.030
You're all the time sticking on
to your aunt — what is it?"

00:47:53.030 --> 00:48:00.740
The concern — and they understand
that it is for their benevolence

00:48:00.740 --> 00:48:01.340
you are telling them.

00:48:01.340 --> 00:48:05.810
But you yourself should be alright.

00:48:05.810 --> 00:48:13.550
As a mother one has to be tolerant,
one has to understand,

00:48:13.550 --> 00:48:16.100
but when you have to tell them,
you have to tell them.

00:48:16.100 --> 00:48:23.360
If you think you can tell them sharply,
or maybe in a proper way —

00:48:23.360 --> 00:48:26.510
but the child should know
that you love the child

00:48:26.510 --> 00:48:30.080
and that you love all the children.

00:48:30.080 --> 00:48:33.110
It is very subtle.

00:48:33.110 --> 00:48:40.760
Like I've seen — once I took a child
of one Sahaja Yogi with Me to the market.

00:48:40.760 --> 00:48:43.100
He was asking,
"I'll buy this, I'll buy that,

00:48:43.100 --> 00:48:46.785
I'll buy that" —
everything he wanted to buy.

00:48:46.785 --> 00:48:48.960
I was wondering,
what's wrong with this boy?

00:48:48.960 --> 00:48:54.360
But say if I take my own grandchildren —
they won't buy, nothing.

00:48:54.360 --> 00:48:57.210
Even if you want to buy
two pairs of shoes:

00:48:57.210 --> 00:48:58.260
"No, no, no — one is sufficient."

00:48:58.260 --> 00:48:59.790
If this will be, then only.

00:48:59.790 --> 00:49:01.260
They'll never ask for anything.

00:49:01.260 --> 00:49:09.495
It's a kind of self-esteem.
They don't want anything.

00:49:09.495 --> 00:49:11.070
Same with the wives.

00:49:11.070 --> 00:49:14.520
Wives never ask for anything
from their husband, nothing.

00:49:14.520 --> 00:49:20.760
Nothing. The husband will go on asking,
"Please ask for something."

00:49:21.720 --> 00:49:23.910
No — they don't want anything.

00:49:23.910 --> 00:49:27.868
That is going to be
a Sahaja Yogini —

00:49:27.868 --> 00:49:30.960
a mother, a wife and a Shakti.

00:49:30.960 --> 00:49:38.580
She has no demands.
Nothing she's asking for.

00:49:38.580 --> 00:49:42.000
The one who's a giver —
what is she going to ask?

00:49:42.000 --> 00:49:47.220
The one who is a supplier —
what is she going to ask?

00:49:47.220 --> 00:49:56.250
So I feel sometimes that the left side,
the women's side in Sahaja Yoga,

00:49:56.250 --> 00:49:57.570
is a little bit going down.

00:49:57.570 --> 00:50:02.160
And they have to come up.

00:50:02.160 --> 00:50:05.550
First, meditation — the respect
of the Mother,

00:50:05.550 --> 00:50:09.150
teaching the children how to work out
Sahaja Yoga,

00:50:09.150 --> 00:50:11.100
talking to them about Sahaja Yoga

00:50:11.100 --> 00:50:21.945
and not only about food,
cleanliness, being nice to others —

00:50:21.945 --> 00:50:23.250
how to share things.

00:50:26.830 --> 00:50:33.100
And telling children good stories
that you have heard.

00:50:33.100 --> 00:50:36.790
Telling them what dharma is,
talking to them.

00:50:36.790 --> 00:50:37.840
Having a rapport.

00:50:37.840 --> 00:50:44.500
This is what you have to understand
to make Sahaja Yoga very strong.

00:50:44.500 --> 00:50:49.300
You are the Shakti of Sahaja Yoga —
take it from Me.

00:50:49.300 --> 00:50:53.875
And you have to work it out that way.

00:50:53.875 --> 00:50:57.430
Instead of worrying about
small, small things.

00:50:57.430 --> 00:51:01.150
Sometimes I receive letters
from the ladies —

00:51:01.150 --> 00:51:03.520
sometimes it really pains me.

00:51:03.520 --> 00:51:06.808
I can't understand how they
are Sahaja Yogis.

00:51:12.730 --> 00:51:18.790
Our whole system of Sahaja has to be
a moral system

00:51:18.790 --> 00:51:26.110
that others should see and understand
what we have achieved

00:51:26.110 --> 00:51:28.690
in our day to day life.

00:51:28.690 --> 00:51:35.020
Adi Shakti works in day to day life,
from the smallest things to the highest.

00:51:35.020 --> 00:51:40.960
And all the time you have to learn,
all the time you have to learn.

00:51:40.960 --> 00:51:43.540
Whether you are a leader
or not a leader,

00:51:43.540 --> 00:51:46.810
all the time you must know
what it is you have to know.

00:51:49.840 --> 00:52:01.570
Unless and until you develop
that attitude — I have to learn,

00:52:01.570 --> 00:52:04.015
I have to learn,
still I have to learn —

00:52:04.015 --> 00:52:06.430
this ego will never come.

00:52:06.430 --> 00:52:09.670
Because of this ego
you are satisfied with yourself.

00:52:09.670 --> 00:52:12.580
That's the sign of an ego.

00:52:12.580 --> 00:52:15.310
You don't know how much
you are torturing others,

00:52:15.310 --> 00:52:16.840
what you are destroying — nothing.

00:52:16.840 --> 00:52:20.140
But you feel extremely happy
with yourself.

00:52:20.140 --> 00:52:31.780
Such a happy-go-lucky personality
sometimes lives on air.

00:52:31.780 --> 00:52:37.480
What have I done today
for somebody else?

00:52:37.480 --> 00:52:44.260
How have I talked to somebody else?
What have I given to somebody else?

00:52:44.260 --> 00:52:49.060
I need not give you presents,
there's nothing — why should I?

00:52:49.720 --> 00:52:54.250
But I give you presents
because of My own satisfaction.

00:52:54.250 --> 00:52:59.410
And if I take presents from you,
it is for your own satisfaction.

00:52:59.410 --> 00:53:14.890
So what do we find satisfaction in —
just think about it.

00:53:14.890 --> 00:53:18.820
My house should be alright,
my husband should be alright,

00:53:18.820 --> 00:53:22.810
my children should be alright —
my, my, my.

00:53:23.710 --> 00:53:29.110
Unless and until this "my"
shifts to another person,

00:53:29.110 --> 00:53:35.350
you are still in the realm of maya.

00:53:35.350 --> 00:53:42.520
You have to learn this.

00:53:46.180 --> 00:53:51.775
Think every day — or write,
all of you should write diaries —

00:53:51.775 --> 00:53:56.920
what have I done for others,
what have I said to others,

00:53:56.920 --> 00:54:04.600
what will make or please
another person?

00:54:04.600 --> 00:54:12.190
Small, small things can make
the life so beautiful.

00:54:12.190 --> 00:54:17.230
And also very big things
are there for you.

00:54:19.780 --> 00:54:21.850
If you do not think
that you are very big,

00:54:21.850 --> 00:54:27.145
all these big things
are also for you.

00:54:27.145 --> 00:54:35.860
It's like this — this whole sky
can be covered by one leaf

00:54:35.860 --> 00:54:43.570
if you see the leaf
against the sky.

00:54:43.570 --> 00:54:45.820
The leaf shows its existence.

00:54:45.820 --> 00:54:52.480
In the same way, this whole vision
of Sahaja Yoga

00:54:52.480 --> 00:54:57.640
can be completely covered
by one person

00:55:00.970 --> 00:55:12.610
who stands with this great expanse —
one person here and one person there.

00:55:12.610 --> 00:55:15.400
It's so remarkable.

00:55:15.400 --> 00:55:17.890
It's such a lot of Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:17.890 --> 00:55:24.370
There are people here and there
and there — so remarkable —

00:55:24.370 --> 00:55:32.050
that if you take their names also,
I just feel I'm drenched

00:55:32.050 --> 00:55:34.360
into the ocean of joy.

00:55:34.360 --> 00:55:40.330
Only one person — then what about you?

00:55:40.330 --> 00:55:46.060
Why can't we do that?

00:55:46.060 --> 00:55:53.905
When Adi Shakti is with you reflected —
when all Her powers are with you —

00:55:53.905 --> 00:56:02.440
how much we can do
in this expanse of My vision.

00:56:02.440 --> 00:56:14.740
I want to have more and more people
who will be of some vision themselves.

00:56:14.740 --> 00:56:21.670
But not small people who just think
of their children, think of food.

00:56:21.670 --> 00:56:24.130
No — they are not wanted, useless.

00:56:24.130 --> 00:56:25.900
They will all drop out.

00:56:25.900 --> 00:56:36.610
I hope you have understood
where you are,

00:56:36.610 --> 00:56:38.020
what you have,

00:56:38.020 --> 00:56:43.330
what is created within you —
this Kundalini —

00:56:43.330 --> 00:56:45.730
which has given you all the knowledge
and everything.

00:56:45.730 --> 00:56:48.340
But there are so many I know
who don't even know

00:56:48.340 --> 00:56:50.530
what this chakra is —
they don't know.

00:56:51.700 --> 00:56:53.290
Going to that limit of ignorance.

00:56:53.290 --> 00:56:55.900
You have to know all these things.

00:56:55.900 --> 00:56:59.380
You have to understand what it is

00:56:59.380 --> 00:57:09.700
because this is for you,
all for you, all this knowledge.

00:57:10.500 --> 00:57:16.170
And the greatest of all is the faith —

00:57:16.170 --> 00:57:19.950
not a faith which is blind
but enlightened faith

00:57:19.950 --> 00:57:23.490
that you are now one
with that Divine power.

00:57:23.490 --> 00:57:28.650
This should really settle you
completely.

00:57:31.500 --> 00:57:33.990
I think this is one of the most
important pujas

00:57:33.990 --> 00:57:40.470
because so far there have been
guru pujas,

00:57:40.470 --> 00:57:43.905
and so many people have worshipped
those gurus.

00:57:43.905 --> 00:57:48.000
Or maybe My birthday as you think it be,
it's alright.

00:57:48.000 --> 00:57:54.240
But I think to understand your own powers
of Kundalini

00:57:54.240 --> 00:58:01.380
and your powers that are available
for the working of Paramchaitanya

00:58:01.380 --> 00:58:03.990
is very important.

00:58:03.990 --> 00:58:08.520
That will give you confidence,
that'll give you compassion,

00:58:08.520 --> 00:58:10.320
that'll give you a vision

00:58:10.320 --> 00:58:13.380
and that will make you
a very great personality.

00:58:15.750 --> 00:58:20.370
What was George Washington?
They said he was great.

00:58:21.570 --> 00:58:24.060
What was Abraham Lincoln?
He was great.

00:58:24.060 --> 00:58:27.060
But you are all having
your self-realisation.

00:58:27.060 --> 00:58:35.250
You have to think of the whole universe,
the whole expanse —

00:58:35.250 --> 00:58:37.590
unless and until that brain
develops in you,

00:58:37.590 --> 00:58:45.900
I'm very sure that the progress
of Sahaja Yoga within and without

00:58:45.900 --> 00:58:46.710
will be less.

00:58:46.710 --> 00:58:49.500
So understand — these powers
are with you.

00:58:49.500 --> 00:58:52.560
You have to utilise them,
with humility.

00:58:52.560 --> 00:58:55.230
May God bless you.

